{"tid":2169762,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【激嬲小粉紅】Call of Duty新預告插六四畫面 網民：意識形態輸出有一手","createTime":"2020-08-22T17:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T04:45:52.000Z","uid":51620,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0911163615d282d2482a55d14f01e1c9d214af2b","tid":2169762,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/PSDKP7BHRNFFROBFHRQJ4N5SLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FPSDKP7BHRNFFROBFHRQJ4N5SLE%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6RYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=af1e459b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FPSDKP7BHRNFFROBFHRQJ4N5SLE%2F&h=d97f7c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/PSDKP7BHRNFFROBFHRQJ4N5SLE/</a><br />\n<br />\n知名遊戲《決勝時刻》（Call of Duty）系列，將在本月26日推出最新作品《決勝時刻黑色行動：冷戰》（Call Of Duty Black Ops: Cold War），日前推出預告片，不過並未展示遊戲畫面，反而以很多真實的歷史片段，講述冷戰時期的背景，其中有1秒更是六四事件、學生對抗坦克車的畫面。內地網民批評是遊戲開發商故意輸出意識形態，「政治影響遊戲」，內地當局迅速封殺。前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒欣賞遊戲商的做法；資深時事評論員劉銳紹則認為，當局擔心這畫面會讓民眾聯想到六四前的情況，挑起民怨，所以要在萌芽階段摧毀。"},{"pid":"2257e2bb1649faa01c211fca3a3fb7d011d1f619","tid":2169762,"uid":37443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb67e06524b3977438a26c3ee28e749f88cbb316","tid":2169762,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f249a59918082472a19d123bb703e4ecef02279","tid":2169762,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2257e2bb1649faa01c211fca3a3fb7d011d1f619","tid":2169762,"uid":37443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"